title: TEMPLATE Miniature pumpkin boxes for 1:12 scale dollhouse | PDF
description: Miniature vintage boxes printable template. One A4 sheet contains 10 boxes with different sizes. Please note that the handles for the boxes are made of polymer clay and are not included in the price of the template.
